. Bull. 20 (July 1944). Archived issues are available in digital format as part of the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Merged with: Yuma weekly examiner, to form: Arizona sentinel and Yuma weekly examiner. Yuma weekly examiner Arizona sentinel and Yuma weekly examiner 2166-9775 (DLC)sn 95060876 (OCoLC)33805457"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:07.816Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-12"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84021912/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [32.754863, -111.671103], "location": ["arizona", "yuma", "yuma county", "arizona city", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-111.671103, 32.754863], "number": ["microfilm master", "sharlot hall mus arch & libr", "microfilm service copy", "american antiquarian soc, newsp proj", "sn84021912", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84021912/1872-03-23/ed-1/", "arizona hist found", "2166-1928", "univ of texas at austin", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "1", "yuma cnty libr dist", "2701984", "2025-06-25t14:21:38", "mojave desert heritage & cultural asn", "2025", "arizona state libr, arch & pub records", "arkansas state univ - jonesboro", "the autry museum of the american west", "2023-12-21t07:55:00.444837", "online resource", "wisconsin hist soc, newsp proj", "arizona hist soc, yuma", "univ of arkansas, fayetteville", "library of congress", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84021912/1911-09-21/ed-1/", "original", "sn95060876", "arizona hist soc, s arizona div", "northern arizona univ"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the arizona sentinel (arizona city [yuma], yuma county, a.t. [ariz.]) 1872-1911", "serial and government publications division", "catalog", "chronicling america"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 86.080376, "shelf_id":