ey will differ as much in then definitions as they do as to what constitutes a drunk A modern dude with narrow striped clothes saddle colored shoes aloud necktie hair parted over his nose and smoking a cigarette addressed his best girl thus If you was me and I was you what would you do She hesitatingly said with a smile I would take off that hideous tie put that cigarette in the stove part my hair on one side then prayto God for brains That our American rorests abound In plants which possess the most valuable medicinal virtues is abundantly attested by scores of the most eminent medical writers and teachers Even the untu tored Indians had discovered the useful ness of many native plants before the advent of the white race This informa tion imparted freely to the whites led the latter to continue investigations until today wo Jiavc a rich assortment of most valuable American medicinal roots Dr Pierce believes that our American for ests aUfepd In most valuable medicinal roct3 foa the cmtijf most"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-01-09T14:49:22.858Z", "group": ["ndnp/az", "arizona-state-university-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84021912/1907-11-20/ed-1/?sp=2", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:az:batch_az_fireant_ver01:data:sn84021912:00211104351:1907112001:0298/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=302&w=216", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:az:batch_az_fireant_ver01:data:sn84021912:00211104351:1907112001:0298/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=604&w=432", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/az/batch_az_fireant_ver01/data/sn84021912/00211104351/1907112001/0298.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["arizona", "yuma", "yuma county", "arizona city", "united states"], "location_city": ["yuma", "arizona city"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["yuma"], "location_state"